      <trans-unit id="14215" identifier="d39232f8ecdc31ad06285a8a1912251c">
        <source>Edit your program so it can take any integer (including negative integers) for the power (e.g. \(8^{-2} = \frac{1}{8^{2}} = \frac{1}{64}\)).</source>
        <target>crwdns14215:0{-2}crwdnd14215:0{1}crwdnd14215:0{2}crwdnd14215:0{1}crwdnd14215:0{64}crwdne14215:0</target>
